trans-unit.source: Failed to resolve SDK '{0}'. A package was successfully restored but the package could not be located.
trans-unit.target: '{0}' SDK'sı çözümlenemedi. Bir paket başarıyla geri yüklendi ancak paket bulunamadı.
trans-unit.note: {0} is the name of an MSBuild project SDK.

trans-unit.source: The NuGetSdkResolver did not resolve this SDK because it was disabled by the MSBUILDDISABLENUGETSDKRESOLVER environment variable.
trans-unit.target: NuGetSdkResolver, MSBUILDDISABLENUGETSDKRESOLVER ortam değişkeni tarafından devre dışı bırakıldığından bu SDK'yı çözümlemedi.

trans-unit.source: The NuGetSdkResolver did not resolve this SDK because there was no version specified in the project or global.json.
trans-unit.target: Projede veya global.json'da belirtilen sürüm olmadığından NuGetSdkResolver bu SDK'yı çözümlemedi.

trans-unit.source: Failed to determine path to global.json from path "{0}". {1}
trans-unit.note: {0} is the path to the file used to start looking for global.json and {1} is the exception message that occurred.
{0} is the path to the global.json file that was attempted to be parsed and {1} is the exception message that occurred.
{0} is the path to the global.json file that was attempted to be read and {1} is the exception message that occurred.

trans-unit.source: Failed to resolve SDK '{0}'. Package restore was successful but a package with the ID of "{1}" was not installed.
trans-unit.target: '{0}' SDK'sı çözümlenemedi. Paket geri yükleme başarılı ancak "{1}" kimlikli bir paket yüklü değil.
trans-unit.note: {0} is name of an MSBuild project SDK and {1} is package ID that was installed.
